An Abyssal demon (elite) is an elite version of the abyssal demon. If on a Slayer assignment, an elite Abyssal demon is guaranteed to spawn; otherwise, elite monsters have a spawn rate of 1 in 1,000. Elite spawn rates can be further increased with the use of fellstalk incense sticks and tier 3 luck.
